onChange.script:
import traceback
	try:
		rawData = self.getChild("root").getChild("Table").custom.filteredData
		if rawData != None:
			maxRow = rawData.rowCount
			rows = self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("RowsDropdown").props.value
			page = int(currentValue.value)
			startRow = rows * (page-1)
			endRow = rows * page
			if startRow > 0:
				delList = range(0,startRow)
			else:
				delList = []
			if endRow < maxRow:
				delList.extend(range(endRow,maxRow))
				
			self.getChild("root").getChild("Table").custom.pagedData = system.dataset.deleteRows(rawData,delList)
			
			#Moves the "view window" on the pagination tab container
			iCurTab = self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.currentTabIndex
			maxPage = maxRow / rows
			if iCurTab != 4 and page > 2 and page < maxPage - 2:	
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.tabs[2] = str(page - 2)
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.tabs[3] = str(page - 1)
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.tabs[4] = str(page)
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.tabs[5] = str(page + 1)
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.tabs[6] = str(page + 2)
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.currentTabIndex = 4
			#First
			elif iCurTab == 0:
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.tabs[2] = "1"
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.tabs[3] = "2"
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.tabs[4] = "3"
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.tabs[5] = "4"
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.tabs[6] = "5"
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.currentTabIndex = 2
			#Last
			elif iCurTab == 8:
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.tabs[2] = str(maxPage - 4)
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.tabs[3] = str(maxPage - 3)
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.tabs[4] = str(maxPage - 2)
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.tabs[5] = str(maxPage - 1)
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.tabs[6] = str(maxPage)
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.currentTabIndex = 6
			#Prev for tabs 1 and 2
			elif iCurTab == 1 and page <=2:
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.currentTabIndex = page + 1
			#Next for tab 1
			elif iCurTab == 7 and page <=2:
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.currentTabIndex = page + 1
			#Next for last 2 tabs
			elif iCurTab == 7 and page >= maxPage - 2:
				diff = maxPage - page
				self.getChild("root").getChild("FlexContainer").getChild("TabContainer").props.currentTabIndex = 8 - diff
	except:
		logger = system.util.getLogger("Registrations_Table view.params.selPage OnChange")
		msg = traceback.format_exc()
		logger.error(msg)

messageHandlers.script:
'''
	return
	
	from datetime import datetime, date
	
	if(payload['key'] == 'gender'):
		curFilter = str(self.view.params.gender)
		#If checkbox is checked, we're adding the payload
		if(payload['state']):
			#If not default, need to do on-purpose SQL injection
			if(curFilter != '%'):
				self.view.params.gender = curFilter + "%' OR [humans].[Human].[gender] LIKE '" + str(payload['val']) 
			#Else, it's default, just set the value
			else:
				self.view.params.gender = str(payload['val'])
		#If checkbox isn't checked, we're removing the payload
		else:
			#If we already have a SQL injection, we need to remove the selected query
			if('LIKE' in curFilter):
				self.view.params.gender = curFilter.replace("%' OR [humans].[Human].[gender] LIKE '" + str(payload['val']), '')
			#If no SQL injection, set to default
			else:
				self.view.params.gender = '%'
	elif(payload['key'] == 'dobRange'):
		curStartDate = str(self.view.params.startDOB)
		curEndDate = str(self.view.params.endDOB)
		
		today = datetime.now()
		#If 55+ is selected, force it to 55-120
		ageRange = payload['val'].replace('+','-120')
		dashPtr = str(ageRange).find('-')
		
		startAge = int(ageRange[0:dashPtr])
		endAge = int(ageRange[dashPtr + 1:])
		#Start date is now minus end age. End date is now minus start age
		#I would like to confess I spent 3 entire minutes remembering how dates worked on this part
		newStartDOB = today.replace(year = datetime.now().year - endAge)
		newEndDOB = today.replace(year = datetime.now().year - startAge)
		
		#If checkbox is checked, we're adding the payload
		if(payload['state']):
			#If not default, need to do on-purpose SQL injection
			#Note, added if not self check because saw weird instance where this happened from clicking too fast
			if(curEndDate != "2110-01-01" and  curEndDate != newEndDOB.strftime("%Y-%m-%d")):
				newEndQueryStr = curEndDate + "' OR [humans].[Human].[dob] BETWEEN '" + newStartDOB.strftime("%Y-%m-%d") + "' AND '" + newEndDOB.strftime("%Y-%m-%d")
				self.view.params.startDOB = curStartDate
				self.view.params.endDOB = newEndQueryStr
			#Else, it's default, just add the range
			else:
				self.view.params.startDOB = newStartDOB.strftime("%Y-%m-%d")
				self.view.params.endDOB = newEndDOB.strftime("%Y-%m-%d")
		#If checkbox isn't checked, we're removing the payload
		else:
			#If we already have a SQL injection, we need to remove the selected query
			if('OR [humans]' in curEndDate):
				self.view.params.endDOB = curEndDate.replace("' OR [humans].[Human].[dob] BETWEEN '" + newStartDOB.strftime("%Y-%m-%d") + "' AND '" + newEndDOB.strftime("%Y-%m-%d"), '')
			#If no SQL injection, set to default
			else:
				self.view.params.startDOB = '1910-01-01'
				self.view.params.endDOB = '2110-01-01'
	#Have to refresh the binding for the query to run again with the new query strings in the view params
	self.refreshBinding("props.data")
	
	'''

#Commented Out unitl Filters are fixed
	'''
	self.custom.filters = filters.messageHandler_UpdateFilter(payload, self.custom.filters)
	'''

onChange.script:
system.perspective.print("RowsDropdown.props.value OnChange")
	#   #OLD LOGIC
	curPage = int(self.view.params.selPage)
	if previousValue > currentValue:
		self.view.params.selPage = curPage - 1
	else:
		self.view.params.selPage = curPage + 1	

#	self.view.params.selPage = 3 #Page 1

system.perspective.print("TabContainer.props.currentTabIndex OnChange")
	rawData = self.parent.parent.getChild("Table").custom.filteredData
	prevTab = int(self.view.params.selPage)
	maxTab = rawData.rowCount / self.getSibling("RowsDropdown").props.value
	selTab = self.props.currentTabIndex
	if selTab == 0:
		#"First"
		self.view.params.selPage = 1
	elif selTab == 1 and prevTab > 1:
		#"Prev"
		self.view.params.selPage = prevTab - 1
	elif selTab == 7 and prevTab < maxTab:
		#"Next"
		self.view.params.selPage = prevTab + 1
	elif selTab == 8:
		#"Last"
		self.view.params.selPage = maxTab
	else:
		self.view.params.selPage = self.props.tabs[selTab]
